    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines an HTTP based interface using either JSON or
   CBOR for object encodings for the DRIP Provisioning Agent (DPA) or
   Registry to insert, update or delete information from a DRIP
   Information Agent (DIA).  JSON Web Tokens (JWTs) are used between the
   entities to encapsulate and authenticate the transactions.

	 </t>
